summary: I am an International Business graduate with a passion for Business, cultures, learning new languages and sustainability practices in the business world. I pursued a major in Intercultural Management, which focused on the human power behind corporations. I was fortunate enough to study abroad in Karlstad, Sweden where I have taken courses to satisfy my growing interest in corporate sustainability and develop new skills such as event planning.
